channel.title: What single song blew your mind more than all others?
channel.description:
Pretty consistently I am blown away with how good certain songs are. However, I'd love to hear if there is one song above others that just really "changed everything" for you. For example, for me it was "Grow Fonder" by Pogo:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2CYaZFydbA4
Not only does it have a hauntingly beautiful sound, and capture powerful nostalgia, the sampling is just off the charts, like nothing I've ever heard (besides other Pogo songs). It really just blows my mind, not just techinically, but how soul-stirring it is. I feel like it opens my mind to a whole new world of possibilities.
What song did it for you?
